{"tid":1335601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7.21維園見 但都不要放過新城巿","createTime":"2019-07-20T14:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T15:29:08.000Z","uid":274469,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c256c5bd4a9f9e30381a4a08cefc542a56267339","tid":1335601,"uid":274469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:53:17.000Z","msg":"明天7.21，我地全部去遊行，無人圍新城市廣場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不能放過深紅基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明天是星期日，工人姐姐放假休息，平時佢地係酷熱的環境席地而坐野餐。不如大家早點起身同工人姐姐講，邀請佢地過來新城巿廣場中庭坐，涼住冷氣野餐。我地可以幫佢開個頭先，之後再去維園，大家覺得可行嗎? btw，明天維園見。"},{"pid":"1df221db6fa79238394ce1244c3c85c263c251eb","tid":1335601,"uid":274469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:54:59.000Z","msg":"明天，維園見"},{"pid":"49a8566877b9690cbdaa1b245442031a25eedcf7","tid":1335601,"uid":274469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:29:08.000Z","msg":"我聽日就拎住一疊meno紙通街派比賓賓，印傭，叫佢黎新城市廣場周圍貼同涼冷氣野餐"}]}